<HEAD>First Palestinian Ambassador Presents Credentials in Algeria</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto PAR5</HEAD>
<DATELINE>ALGIERS, Algeria (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The government has accepted the
credentials of the first ambassador of the newly declared state of
