<HEAD>Gang Member Opens Fire Inside Crowded Mall, Fatally Wounding Teen
Bystander</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: LEADS with 4 grafs to UPDATE with teen dying of wound. Picks
up 4th graf pvs, `The intended...'. Adds one graf with detail on
