<HEAD>Quayles To Cap Ski Vacation at Fiesta Bowl</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Vice President-elect Dan Quayle and his family
leave Wednesday for a 12-day ski vacation in Colorado and will
finish their trip with a quick dash south for the Fiesta Bowl.
   Quayle, his wife Marilyn and their three children will fly from
